{"word":"συννεφέω","slug":"συννεφέω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>συννεφέω</b></el> <el>(<a href='S:perfect tense'>perf.</a> <el>-νένοφα</el>) </el><p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to collect clouds</i>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b>:—<a href='S:impersonal'>impers.</a> <el>συννεφεῖ</el> <i>it is cloudy</i> (<a href='S:confer, compare'>cf.</a> <el>ὕει</el>), <b><a href='S:Aristotle'>Arist.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><a href='S:metaphorically'>metaph.</a> of persons, <el>συννεφοῦσα ὄμματα</el> <i>wearing a clouded</i> look, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/></div><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>from <a href='S:συννεφής'><el>συννεφής</el></a>\n"}]}